data.title: Pasatiempo
data.meta_description: Santa Fe's Weekly Magazine of Arts, Entertainment and Culture
data.text:
Attending the Santa Fe Indian Market is a reminder that our homeland has thrived on a glorious array of people and their cultures, talents, and beliefs. In gathering here, we acknowledge the generosity of our relatives, the Kiis'anii, Pueblos, on whose land we meet, live, create, and celebrate.
